江农林大学</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">2017年英语写作大赛暨</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">2017</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">年</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\"> “外研社杯”全国英语写作大赛</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">校内选拔赛。获奖选手将代表我校参加</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">2017</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">年</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">10</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">月在浙江大学</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">举行的复赛。本次赛事由外国语学院承办。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 7px 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top-alt: auto;margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\"></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;font-weight: bold\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold\">二、比赛安排</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 7px 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top-alt: auto;margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px;font-weight: bold\"></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">1、初赛时间：2017年5月25日（第14周周四）14:00－15:00。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 7px 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top-alt: auto;margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">2、初赛地点：东湖校区学10303\\</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">衣锦校区教学楼</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">811 </span></span> &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 7px 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top-alt: auto;margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);line-height: 150%;font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">3、初赛题目：赛题为议论文写作1篇，长度500词左右，写作时间为1小时。比赛题目在赛前严格保密。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 7px 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top-alt: auto;margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">4、</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">初赛方式：现场写作，比赛不允许携带电子设备，不允许使用网络。</span></span> &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 7px 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.5em;text-indent: 2em;margin-top-alt: auto;margin-bottom-alt: auto\"><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);font-family: 宋体,simsun;font-size: 18px\">5、评分方式： 机器+人工评阅（两项成绩相加得出每位选手总分）。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 7px